content:
Quisi finishes her story "... and just when I thought it was empty, I found the treasure! It wasn't in the box. The box was the treasure!"

RANGERS CHOOSE

A) Continue to help Quisi find her father. Discard all   from Quisi. Each Ranger soothes 1 fatigue. Help her track down her father, Harlan Vos.

B) Good luck, kid! Discard Quisi. Each Ranger soothes 2 fatigue.
